1. 在APP目录中解压文件

2. 在app目录下创建文件夹tmp

3. 编译libid3tag-0.15.1b
    cd libid3tag-0.15.1b
    ./configure --host=arm-linux --prefix=/home/shuimu/more/LinuxDriver/23_Player/app/tmp/
    make
    make install

4. 编译libmad-0.15.1b
       cd libid3tag-0.15.1b
       ./configure --host=arm-linux --prefix=/home/shuimu/more/LinuxDriver/23_Player/app/tmp/
       make
       make install

5. 编译madplayer
    
